description: This Thai chicken noodle curry recipe will help you have dinner on the table in no time. The chicken dish is easy to make with only four ingredients needed.
keywords: Curry,May 2020,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,Low salt,Jun 2020,Low sugar,Chicken,Sesame free
name: Speedy Thai Chicken Noodle Curry Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat curry according to packet instructions. Meanwhile, heat 1 tbs vegetable oil in a wok over high heat. Stir-fry veggies for 2 minutes.
Add curry to vegetables and stir to combine.
Add coconut milk and stir over medium-high heat for 4 minutes or until vegetables are tender.
Meanwhile, cook noodles according to packet instructions. Drain. Divide noodles among bowls and top with curry.
